title: Kevin Millar & Sean Casey | Rex Tillerson Called Trump a Moron: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at the aftermath of President Trump's disastrous response to the humanitarian crisis in Puerto Rico, and a simmering feud with his secretary of state. (0:20)
Then, Seth interviews MLB analysts Kevin Millar and Sean Casey.  (11:16)
Exclusively for this podcast, he continues the conversation backstage at Studio 8G. (19:21)
